rings. The sign change of superconducting\norder parameters on Fermi surfaces is not a necessary requirement in\nrepulsive-interaction-driven high T_c mechanism. The results will guide us to\nsearch for new electronic structure that supports high T_c superconductivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2015 19:55:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-10"}
