tonians, and these will be derived for the potential obtained here\nin a forthcoming paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2015 19:57:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Jun 2015 19:59:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 15 Dec 2015 09:20:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2020 18:20:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
