al signature we find\nis that small haloes residing in the outskirts are more deficient in baryons\nthan their $\\Lambda$CDM counterparts. The lack of a pronounced signal for a\ncoupled dark sector strongly suggests that such a phenomena would be\neffectively hidden from view.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jun 2015 05:12:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
