h gives rise to a mirror seeing of 0.23 arcsec K--1 . We propose\nsolutions to mitigate these effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jun 2015 14:07:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-12"}
